            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>rice noodles</strong> to a pot and cover them with<strong> boiled water </strong>until fully submerged</p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 7-8 min or until tender</p><p>Once done, drain, stir through a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and set aside</p><p>Tip: The oil will stop the noodles from sticking together!</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
