    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the noodles are cooking, dissolve the <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>in 200ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [400ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>with the <strong>creamed coconut</strong> – this is your <strong>coconut stock</strong></p>",
