      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong> and<strong> chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to the pan and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p>",
