      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the prawns are cooking, chop the <strong>coriander</strong> roughly, including the stalks (reserve some leaves for garnish!)</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped coriander</strong>,<strong> rice vinegar </strong>and<strong> lime leaf<span class=\"text-danger\">[ves]</span></strong> to the pan and mix everything together – these are your <strong>Thai-style king prawns & squash</strong></p>",
